    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Pristine and absolutely stunning \u2014 this is the one you've been waiting for! This car is in mint condition, meaning it presents as virtually flawless inside and out, with a spotless interior, gleaming exterior, and everything running and looking exactly as it should. Whether you're a discerning daily driver or a collector who demands the best, this vehicle delivers an ownership experience that's truly rare to find. Don't miss your chance to own a car that's as close to perfect as it gets!",
