    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Ready for a ride you can count on? This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it starts right up, runs smoothly, and handles with confidence on the road. It's been well cared for and shows it, with no major issues to worry about. A solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for real value without compromise!",
      "price": 31500.0,
